name: Home
description:
Home.

The runes in this design reads "hemma är här - här är hemma" (english: "home is here - here is home". The runes are written in an ancient futhark, the oldest runes found in Sweden today have been dated about 400 AD. 

The design itself is made with paper and pens by myself.

Hand printed by myself, the print is of great quality transparent ink.
The sweatshirt is of dark heather 100% certified organic cotton. The feel of this garment is very satisfying and warm. You won't want to take it off once it's on. 

We recommend that you turn your garment inside out 
Wash at 30 degrees with like colours and hang dry 
Do not tumble dry
